parameters.name: EndBounceTime
parameters.description: End time of the last bounce hit, timestamp, accurate to the second. The span between start and end times cannot exceed 7 days.

parameters.name: EndCreateTime
parameters.description: End creation time, timestamp, accurate to the second. The span between start and end times cannot exceed 7 days.

parameters.name: StartBounceTime
parameters.description: Start time of the last bounce hit, timestamp, accurate to the second.

parameters.name: StartCreateTime
parameters.description: Start creation time, timestamp, accurate to the second.
